Description: 2009 Gibson Custom Jimmy Page Signature "Number Two" Les Paul VOS2009 Gibson Custom Jimmy Page Signature “Number Two” Les Paul #058. This guitar, made in collaboration with Jimmy Page, is an authentic replica of his famous “Number Two” Les Paul Burst. Features a “Page Burst” in Gibson’s lightly worn VOS finish, giving it that perfectly broken in feel. This guitar is in excellent, mint condition with the original sticker still on the pickguard! The neck is slim and fast, just like Jimmy’s, which was originally shaved down to match the profile of his beloved “Number One” Les Paul. The custom Jimmy Page Burstbuckers have a lovely vintage PAF sound and feature his signature wiring with series/parallel and coil-split switches hidden underneath the pickguard, providing a wide range of tonal variety. This is an awesome Les Paul and a must have for Page fans! Includes original hardshell case and all original paperwork.
